<div id="review_3056747186" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3056747186" />
    <a title="Germaine Knowlan" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/29024682-germaine-knowlan"><img alt="Germaine Knowlan" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1542246522p2/29024682.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3056747186?book_show_action=true">Nov 21, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Germaine Knowlan" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Germaine Knowlan" href="/user/show/29024682-germaine-knowlan">Germaine Knowlan</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/34993287-the-summer-letters">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3056747186" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer954525948068929390"><strong>A truly must-read book</strong><br/><br/>This lovely storyline has left me speechless. Every line was a page turner. There wasn’t anything in the storyline that I did not like. It was magical, heartwarming, very sad at times and so beautifully written. I have read every one of Elise Douglas’ books; all have been excellent especially the time travel books but “The Summer Letters” is by far my top favorite.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


