<span id="freeTextContainer17209374824225125878"><strong>Book reviee</strong><br/><br/>The book caught my attention quickly, but then became very repetitive and drawn out. Some things made no sense. If someone has been ruled deceased,why did the spouse follow-up with a divorce? I was initially with the impression that Karen and Vanessa&apos; s lives were linked, but, that was not the case. It was not even remotely close. Had it not been for the last chapter in this book, I would have felt even more disappointed.</span>
