<span id="freeTextContainer7478787933915946634"><strong>💜MY NEW FAVORITE AUTHOR💜</strong><br/><br/>I&apos;ve read 6 of their books now, most all of the time travel ones ~ which I thought were my favorite until I read this book! They&apos;re all wonderful and leave you wanting more! The characters are strong and you want to learn more about them as you route for the underdog and wish you could kill off the bad guys yourself.</span>
